08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ms. Khelif\", \"from\": 628, \"to\": 638}, {\"ngram\": \"the firm\", \"from\": 649, \"to\": 657}, {\"ngram\": \"a complaint\", \"from\": 671, \"to\": 682}, {\"ngram\": \"acts\", \"from\": 697, \"to\": 701}, {\"ngram\": \"aggravated cyber harassment\", \"from\": 705, \"to\": 732}, {\"ngram\": \"the anti-online hatred center\", \"from\": 738, \"to\": 767}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris prosecutor's office told ESPN it had not yet received the complaint, although it could come as early as Monday.\", \"from\": 811, \"to\": 932, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 815, \"end\": 820, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999304068321, \"rank\": 6.959307453160038e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 846, \"end\": 850, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\", \"score\": 0.999999998417934, \"rank\": 1.5783068412616803e-09, \"text\": \"ESPN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the complaint\", \"from\": 875, \"to\": 888}, {\"ngram\": \"Monday\", \"from\": 925, \"to\": 931}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Boudi added he asked for the criminal investigation to determine who initiated the \\\"misogynistic, racist and sexist campaign\\\" against Khelif.\", \"from\": 934, \"to\": 1075, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Boudi\", \"from\": 934, \"to\": 939}, {\"ngram\": \"the criminal investigation\", \"from\": 959, \"to\": 985}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"misogynistic, racist and sexist campaign\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1058}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 1068, \"to\": 1074}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The unfair harassment suffered by the boxing champion will remain the biggest stain of these Olympic Games,\\\" Boudi added.\", \"from\": 1077, \"to\": 1199, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The unfair harassment\", \"from\": 1078, \"to\": 1099}, {\"ngram\": \"the boxing champion\", \"from\": 1112, \"to\": 1131}, {\"ngram\": \"the biggest stain\", \"from\": 1144, \"to\": 1161}, {\"ngram\": \"these Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1184}, {\"ngram\": \"Boudi\", \"from\": 1187, \"to\": 1192}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fans have embraced Khelif in Paris even as she faced an extraordinary amount of scrutiny from world leaders, major celebrities and others who have questioned her eligibility or falsely claimed she was a man.\", \"from\": 1201, \"to\": 1408, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1230, \"end\": 1235, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999304068321, \"rank\": 6.959307453160038e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Fans\", \"from\": 1201, \"to\": 1205}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 1220, \"to\": 1226}, {\"ngram\": \"an extraordinary amount\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1277}, {\"ngram\": \"scrutiny\", \"from\": 1281, \"to\": 1289}, {\"ngram\": \"world leaders\", \"from\": 1295, \"to\": 1308}, {\"ngram\": \"major celebrities\", \"from\": 1310, \"to\": 1327}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 1332, \"to\": 1338}, {\"ngram\": \"her eligibility\", \"from\": 1359, \"to\": 1374}, {\"ngram\": \"a man\", \"from\": 1402, \"to\": 1407}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It has thrust her into a larger divide over changing attitudes toward gender identity and regulations in sports.\", \"from\": 1409, \"to\": 1521, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a larger divide\", \"from\": 1432, \"to\": 1447}, {\"ngram\": \"attitudes\", \"from\": 1462, \"to\": 1471}, {\"ngram\